I have similar issue with here.

When I convert tf.keras model (containing tf.keras.layers.Embeddings) -> TF graph -> TF Lite model, The process of tf.keras to TF graph works, but when I convert TF graph to TF Lite, it calls import_graph_def() function internally and causes same error.

Any help would be appreciated.

body:
I have similar issue with here.

When I convert tf.keras model (containing `tf.keras.layers.Embeddings`) -> TF graph -> TF Lite model, The process of tf.keras to TF graph works, but when I convert TF graph to TF Lite, it calls `import_graph_def()` function internally and causes same error.

Any help would be appreciated.
